{"tid":2335643,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"外電指馬雲曾提出將螞蟻部份業務進貢予共產黨 但最終仍無法令集團成功上市","createTime":"2020-12-22T04:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T08:29:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8eaea39b22539d127de223bf252924133c5d0d","tid":2335643,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"外電指馬雲曾提出將螞蟻部份業務交予中國政府<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團臨上市前煞停AH股上市計劃，華爾街日報引述消息人士指，阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d1236376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)、螞蟻集團創辦人馬雲在上月初被監管當局約談期間，曾提出將螞蟻集團部份業務交給中國政府，但最終仍無法令螞蟻集團成功上市。報道指，馬雲在會面中表明只要國家有需要，可以拿走螞蟻這些平台，試圖修復與中國政府關係。<br />\n<br />\n報道又稱，中央未決定是否接受馬雲的提議，當局正考慮要求螞蟻接受更嚴格的監管，包括國有銀行或其他類型的國有投資者將入股螞蟻集團，彌補收緊監管後可能出現的資本缺口。螞蟻集團發言人指，無法證實與監管部門會晤的細節。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2371692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2371692&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=379163a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2371692</a>"},{"pid":"231b44182d940223ba50665907af42eca3e1824e","tid":2335643,"uid":31200,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"部分梗係唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4b3cf6e55762072051462342c6424619e28f3d","tid":2335643,"uid":77717,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"231b44182d940223ba50665907af42eca3e1824e","tid":2335643,"uid":31200,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"部分梗係唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"共產黨：我全要<img src=\